Regulation of transfers of Maharashtra Government employees and in the discharge of government duties.
As per Section 4 (1), 4 (2) and 4 (3) of the Prevention of Delay Act, 2005, the following are mentioned:
Assistant Room Officer / Clerk-Typewriters in the Ministries Division, Column-6 in front of their name

2. Allow the above officers / employees to join the General Administration Department. 05.05.2025

GOVERNMENT ORDER NUMBER: TRANSFER 2025 / Q.No.42 / PRASHT-3
